[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_169435_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/169435/2021_169435_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "This is precisely my situation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_169435_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/169435/2021_169435_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "I have a strong propensity in me to begin this chapter very nonsensically, and I will not balk my fancy.--Accordingly I set off thus:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_169435_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/169435/2021_169435_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "There are others again, who will draw a man's character from no other helps in the world, but merely from his evacuations;--but this often gives a very incorrect outline,--unless, indeed, you take a sketch of his repletions too; and by correcting one drawing from the other, compound one good figure out of them both.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_169435_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/169435/2021_169435_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "I should have no objection to this method, but that I think it must smell too strong of the lamp,--and be render'd still more operose, by forcing you to have an eye to the rest of his Non naturals.--Why the most natural actions of a man's life should be called his Non naturals,--is another question.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235244_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235244/2021_235244_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Chapter two.sixteen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235244_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235244/2021_235244_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Of the qualities and conditions of Panurge.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235244_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235244/2021_235244_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Panurge was of a middle stature, not too high nor too low, and had somewhat an aquiline nose, made like the handle of a razor.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235244_000005_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235244/2021_235244_000005_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Very often, also, upon the women's French hoods would he stick in the hind part somewhat made in the shape of a man's member.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235244_000005_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235244/2021_235244_000005_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "In another, he had a squib furnished with tinder, matches, stones to strike fire, and all other tackling necessary for it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235244_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235244/2021_235244_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "In another, he had a good deal of needles and thread, wherewith he did a thousand little devilish pranks.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235244_000006_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235244/2021_235244_000006_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Nay, saint Anthony's fire kiss it for us!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235244_000006_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235244/2021_235244_000006_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "For, according to the Legists, agitation and continual motion is cause of attraction.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235244_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235244/2021_235244_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Others, again, ran about the streets, and he would run after them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235244_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235244/2021_235244_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "To such as were in the stripping vein he would very civilly come to offer his attendance, and cover them with his cloak, like a courteous and very gracious man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235244_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235244/2021_235244_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Madam, God give you all that your noble heart desireth!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235244_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235244/2021_235244_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Another he had all full of euphorbium, very finely pulverized.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235244_000009_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235244/2021_235244_000009_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "No, no, madam, said he, I do but tune my tail to the plain song of the music which you make with your nose.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235244_000009_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235244/2021_235244_000009_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "In another he had a picklock, a pelican, a crampiron, a crook, and some other iron tools, wherewith there was no door nor coffer which he would not pick open.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235244_000009_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235244/2021_235244_000009_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "He had another full of little cups, wherewith he played very artificially, for he had his fingers made to his hand, like those of Minerva or Arachne, and had heretofore cried treacle.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235245_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235245/2021_235245_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "For my part, I gained no more of them, but he at all the boxes kissed the relics, and gave at everyone.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235245_000003_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235245/2021_235245_000003_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Unto which he answered me that he had taken it out of the basins of the pardons.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235245_000003_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235245/2021_235245_000003_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "For in giving them the first farthing, said he, I put it in with such sleight of hand and so dexterously that it appeared to be a threepence; thus with one hand I took threepence, ninepence, or sixpence at the least, and with the other as much, and so through all the churches where we have been.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235245_000003_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235245/2021_235245_000003_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "It was worth to me above six thousand florins, in English coin six hundred pounds.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235245_000003_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235245/2021_235245_000003_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "They returned from whence they came, said he; they did no more but change their master.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235245_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235245/2021_235245_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "By this means, to one I gave a hundred florins, to another six score, to another three hundred, according to that they were infamous, detestable, and abominable.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235245_000004_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235245/2021_235245_000004_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Then began the poor rogues to gape like old mules, and I caused to be provided for them a banquet, with drink of the best, and store of spiceries, to put the old women in rut and heat of lust.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235245_000004_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235245/2021_235245_000004_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "To be short, they occupied all, like good souls; only, to those that were horribly ugly and ill favoured, I caused their head to be put within a bag, to hide their face.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235245_000005_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235245/2021_235245_000005_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "And for this I had a fair decree, but it cost me dear.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235245_000005_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235245/2021_235245_000005_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "And to what end? said i My friend, said he, thou hast no pastime at all in this world.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_235245_000005_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/235245/2021_235245_000005_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "I have more than the king, and if thou wilt join thyself with me, we will do the devil together.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "THE CURATE'S COUNSEL.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Not seeing yet what he had to say, but knowing that scintillation the smallest is light, the curate let the talk take its natural course, and said the next thing that came to him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"How do you feel when you think that you may yet be found out?\" he asked.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Then after that danger seemed past, I was afraid of the life to come.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "That fear left me next, and now it is the thing itself that is always haunting me. I often wish they would come and take me, and deliver me from myself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000004_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000004_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "It would be a comfort to have it all known, and never need to start again.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000004_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000004_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "I would, indeed, mr Wingfold.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"I do believe you,\" said the curate, and a silence followed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000006_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000006_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "And I do think, if we could find him, then we should find help.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000006_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000006_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "All I can do for you now is only to be near you, and talk to you, and pray to God for you, that so together we may wait for what light may come.--Does anything ever look to you as if it would make you feel better?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"Oh, yes, indeed I do!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"I don't know.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "It seems a sneaking kind of thing: she has got none of it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "My sister makes excuses for me, but the moment I begin to listen to them I only feel the more horrid.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"I have said nothing of that kind to you.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"Yes, indeed, sir,\" he answered, earnestly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "It makes me feel it worse than ever to see you sitting there, a clean, strong, innocent man, and think what I might have been.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"Then the comfort you get from me does you no harm, at least.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "I have come to see-at least I think I have-that except a man has God dwelling in him, he may be, or may become, capable of any crime within the compass of human nature.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"I don't know anything about God,\" said Leopold.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"Ah, Leopold!\" said the curate, \"think, if my coming to you comforts you, what would it be to have him who made you always with you!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"Where would be the good?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Why should you not be ashamed?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000024_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000024_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Why would you have the shame taken off you?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000024_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000024_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Let us keep our shame, and be made clean from the filth!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000025_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000025_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Is it not to have done the deed that is the defilement?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"Is it not rather to have that in you, a part, or all but a part of your being, that makes you capable of doing it?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "If you had resisted and conquered, you would have been clean from it; and now, if you repent and God comes to you, you will yet be clean.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Again I say, let us keep our shame and be made clean!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000026_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000026_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "On the contrary, the man who is honestly ashamed has begun to be clean.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"But what good would that do to Emmeline?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"Emmeline is not in the dark grave.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"Where is she, then?\" he said with a ghastly look.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"That I cannot tell.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000031_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000031_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "How was such a poor passionate creature to take that for a comfort?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000031_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000031_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "How was he to understand or prize the idea, who had his spiritual nature so all undeveloped?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000031_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000031_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "He would try another way.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"I think sometimes, if I could but see Jesus for one moment-\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"YOU would like to see him then, would you?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"What would you say to him if you saw him?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"I don't know.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000039_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000039_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "I would fall down on my face and hold his feet lest he should go away from me.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "\"Yes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000041_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000041_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "He could destroy what I have done.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2021_246946_000045_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2021/246946/2021_246946_000045_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2021",
        "content": "Don't you?\" said Leopold with an amazed, half frightened look.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
